name: Infinite Cycle of Life
description: A compilation of oracular energy spheres that mirrors the birth, death and rebirth of the soul. This series is a serendipitous discovery which is a result of a miscalculation of formulas in search of the Mandelbrot Fractals. I filtered countless of images and compiled 300 frames of enigmatic energy spheres that resembles an infinite cycle of life. The series includes Destruction, Rebirth, Conception and the "Infinite Cycle of Life".
